{"chunk_id": "github_pr_1425_comment_2110003047", "source_type": "reviews", "pairs": [{"instruction": "Can you review this approach: I added an explicit import for `argparse.zig` into the main module's public namespace to provide functionality for parsing command-line arguments.", "response": "Adding a new entry to the public API surface without documentation can be confusing or misleading for users of the library. Please insert a doc comment block that states 'Provides functionality for parsing command-line arguments' and clarifies that it is part of the public API. This ensures discoverability and proper usage expectations."}], "user_id": "Nick"}
